Well you know what the usual routine was then for children sugar peg cost a penny, an orange, apple, a new penny if possible, a new penny if possible, and just one or two nu
ts and that was put in your stocking. Orange, apple, a new penny if possible, with a sugar pig. Sugar pig. Orange, apple, a new penny if possible and just one or two nuts. We used to put the stocking up on the bedrail you know, and me mother used to put t
hem in. when we were asleep. And that was Christmas. No toys.
