No, not that I know of. I never recollect having any - not when me mother was a widow. Though things did improve in that line when she married again, we got better fo
od no doubt, we did get better food. But as I say, things didn't turn out, there was a lot of unpleasantness and all like that you know really until the family, they went, sort of style.
